{"tid":532452,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"3年嚟只係得感情冇愛情","createTime":"2018-01-18T00:38:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T17:04:11.000Z","uid":95069,"like":11,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"77dc8a392a7f3bc5ca25bb5a629e13b2e72a0d66","tid":532452,"uid":95069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:38:46.000Z","msg":"三年嚟 我一直都喺活喺你嘅大話之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來唔止偷食過一次 原來有四次 <br />\n第一次被分手我選擇咗原諒你 因為我心軟我蠢我未見過你喊得咁傷心以為你真喺知錯會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二次被分手我又再次選擇原諒你 就算分開咗你仲喺好關心我 當時我總喺覺得你有苦衷有啲野諗唔通 所以我決定原地等你返嚟我身邊 幾個月後終於俾我等到<br />\n之後嘅日子你一日比一日愛錫我 一日比一日對我好 <br />\n我以為你已經改過 我亦都好努力為你變得更成熟 <br />\n你同我傾買樓結婚嗰時係點 帶我去見你屋企人 我以為你唔會再離開我 以為我地喺會行到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最後我發覺原來全部都喺假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換黎嘅喺你話呢三年你覺得好厭倦 只喺得感情無拍拖嘅感覺 你扮好人扮得好辛苦<br />\n我覺得你好陌生 我心真喺好痛。"},{"pid":"cf8bcab9cfdb578cc4cef161824fa13f0e8df5c7","tid":532452,"uid":72226,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5eb9c13826fb20e32387bb4630b8f3ee7bc65e1","tid":532452,"uid":36820,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"做咩啫你"},{"pid":"76b464275b5f3cec9e0f224defd325338ce353ed","tid":532452,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:41:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"21a305fa491858a752b6b39fb06b5dcb6be9c63d","tid":532452,"uid":95069,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"cf8bcab9cfdb578cc4cef161824fa13f0e8df5c7","tid":532452,"uid":72226,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:40:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:42:09.000Z","msg":"我都覺得我喺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"345ebd6d2abe9dc96b0051813c6f25288eeaf501","tid":532452,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":11,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:42:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d07ee113c6bb41adefd9717fdd8fba3bb15b6ee2","tid":532452,"uid":131553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"5 年<br />\n最後一句感情淡了<br />\n就byebye<br />\n好明你感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f98ffd57fb1a48906aea7c62366ae7175557699","tid":532452,"uid":95069,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d07ee113c6bb41adefd9717fdd8fba3bb15b6ee2","tid":532452,"uid":131553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:44:26.000Z","msg":"5 年<br />\n最後一句感情淡了<br />\n就byebye<br />\n好明你感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48471f7b925d97426b33830fa2df56bc68b57f3e","tid":532452,"uid":104828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-18T00:50:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三年嚟 我一直都喺活喺你嘅大話之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來唔止偷食過一次 原來有四次 <br />\n第一次被分手我選擇咗原諒你 因為我心軟我蠢我未見過你喊得咁傷心以為你真喺知錯會後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二次被分手我又再次選擇原諒你 就算分開咗你仲喺好關心我 當時我總喺覺得你有苦衷有啲野諗唔通 所以我決定原地等你返嚟我身邊 幾個月後終於俾我等到<br />\n之後嘅日子你一日比一日愛錫我 一日比一日對我好 <br />\n我以為你已經改過 我亦都好努力為你變得更成熟 <br />\n你同我傾買樓結婚嗰時係點 帶我去見你屋企人 我以為你唔會再離開我 以為我地喺會行到尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但最後我發覺原來全部都喺假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n換黎嘅喺你話呢三年你覺得好厭倦 只喺得感情無拍拖嘅感覺 你扮好人扮得好辛苦<br />\n我覺得你好陌生 我心真喺好痛。</blockquote><br />\n點解一個好女仔總會遇到唔好嘅男人"},{"pid":"a1696a6b831deabc6cdd53f29b733d97921fd611","tid":532452,"uid":95069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"